author: Telegraph Staff
title: The Old Clare Hotel, Sydney, Australia - in pictures
text:
MORE... 
Sydney welcomes a new hotel to the fray this month. Part of the Unlisted Collection and the vision of hotelier Loh Lik Peng, The Old Clare Hotel will be a buzzing hub in the artsy district of Chippendale, with a huge focus on food and drink, and a sure-to-be desirable rooftop pool.
